author: Russell Brand
description:
Did former FBI Director James Comey post a coded call to assassinate Donald Trump? Russell breaks down the controversy around Comey’s now-deleted “8647” Instagram post—allegedly referencing “86” (get rid of) and Trump as the 47th president. With assassination attempts fresh in the public mind, figures like Tulsi Gabbard and Trump himself weigh in. Is this just bad judgment, or something far more sinister?
